questions.quote: C'mon, seriously, you guys, you're not going to make me watch this alone!
I was giving you an appology and you were totally checking her out!
And I'm blah? Listen, the only thing more boring than watching modern dance is having to listen to you talk about it, "Oh Chandler, I just lost myself in the moment."
I'm guessing your new girlfriend wouldn't urinate on my coffee table.
In the future, when a girl asks for some ill-advised sympathy sex... just do it.
Oh honey, this is his office too. I told you we're Joanna's two assistants.
And I have your name and the fact that you're a drifter, so the ball's pretty much in your court.
So, whaddya say boys, should I call him? Well, ya know what they say. Ask your slippers a question... you're going crazy.
No-no-no! I am the king of bad Thanksgivings. You can't just swoop in here with your bad marriage and take that away from me.
Okay fine! Fine! We'll just have to think of some other way to put the whole 'Who came onto who,' thing to rest! Come on now, think!!
